      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. GEORGIA SKIES broke through for her maiden success two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished fifth and beaten 11 lengths at this track over 520m (30.91). Returns to the course where she won her maiden. Better than latest and can atone here. 2. PROWL has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (26.03) last time in a Grade 6 at Q Lakeside. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Should be thereabouts. 8. ASTON TOLHURST got off the mark last time, scoring by one length at Capalaba over 366m (19.94). Will break from a wide draw. Harder here but expected to feature again. 1. REGAL MALT will make his presence felt on the back of recent top-three finishes.\",\"runners\":[4,2,8,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
